{"heading":[["1–6","scripture-ref","dc-testament/dc/133.1-6"],", The Saints are commanded to prepare for the Second Coming; ",["7–16","scripture-ref","dc-testament/dc/133.7-16"],", All men are commanded to flee from Babylon, come to Zion, and prepare for the great day of the Lord; ",["17–35","scripture-ref","dc-testament/dc/133.17-35"],", He will stand on Mount Zion, the continents will become one land, and the lost tribes of Israel will return; ",["36–40","scripture-ref","dc-testament/dc/133.36-40"],", The gospel was restored through Joseph Smith to be preached in all the world; ",["41–51","scripture-ref","dc-testament/dc/133.41-51"],", The Lord will come down in vengeance upon the wicked; ",["52–56","scripture-ref","dc-testament/dc/133.52-56"],", It will be the year of His redeemed; ",["57–74","scripture-ref","dc-testament/dc/133.57-74"],", The gospel is to be sent forth to save the Saints and for the destruction of the wicked."],"number":133,"verseCount":74,"verses":[[1,["Hearken, O ye people of my church, saith the Lord your God, and hear the word of the Lord concerning you—"]],[2,["The Lord who shall suddenly ",["come",["study-note-ref","a",[["Mal. 3:1","ot/mal/3.1"],"; ",["D&C 36:8","dc-testament/dc/36.8"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Second Coming","tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"],"."]]]," to his temple; the Lord who shall come down upon the world with a curse to ",["judgment",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 1:36","dc-testament/dc/1.36"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Judge","tg/jesus-christ-judge"],"; ",["Judgment, the Last","tg/judgment-the-last"],"."]]],"; yea, upon all the nations that ",["forget",["study-note-ref","c",[["2 Kgs. 17:38","ot/2-kgs/17.38"],"; ",["Alma 46:8","bofm/alma/46.8"],"."]]]," God, and upon all the ungodly among you."]],[3,["For he shall make ",["bare",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 52:10","ot/isa/52.10"],". ",["TG God, Power of","tg/god-power-of"],"."]]]," his holy arm in the eyes of all the nations, ",["",274],"and all the ends of the earth shall see the ",["salvation",["study-note-ref","b",[["Isa. 12:2","ot/isa/12.2"],"; ",["52:10","ot/isa/52.10"],". ",["TG Salvation","tg/salvation"],"."]]]," of their God."]],[4,["Wherefore, prepare ye, prepare ye, O my people; sanctify yourselves; gather ye together, O ye people of my church, upon the land of Zion, all you that have not been commanded to ",["tarry",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 62:4","dc-testament/dc/62.4"],"; ",["63:41 (24, 39–41)","dc-testament/dc/63.41"],"."]]],"."]],[5,["Go ye out from ",["Babylon",["study-note-ref","a",[["Alma 5:57","bofm/alma/5.57"],"; ",["D&C 1:16","dc-testament/dc/1.16"],". ",["TG Worldliness","tg/worldliness"],"."]]],". Be ye ",["clean",["study-note-ref","b",[["Isa. 52:11","ot/isa/52.11"],"; ",["2 Tim. 2:21","nt/2-tim/2.21"],"; ",["3 Ne. 20:41","bofm/3-ne/20.41"],"; ",["D&C 38:42","dc-testament/dc/38.42"],". ",["TG Body, Sanctity of","tg/body-sanctity-of"],"; ",["Cleanliness","tg/cleanliness"],"."]]]," that bear the vessels of the Lord."]],[6,["Call your ",["solemn assemblies",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Solemn Assembly","tg/solemn-assembly"],"."]]],", and ",["speak",["study-note-ref","b",[["Mal. 3:16 (16–18)","ot/mal/3.16"],"."]]]," often one to another. And let every man call upon the name of the Lord."]],[7,["Yea, verily I say unto you again, the time has come when the voice of the Lord is unto you: Go ye out of Babylon; ",["gather",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 29:8","dc-testament/dc/29.8"],". ",["TG Israel, Gathering of","tg/israel-gathering-of"],"; ",["Mission of Latter-day Saints","tg/mission-of-latter-day-saints"],"."]]]," ye out from among the nations, from the ",["four",["study-note-ref","b",[["Zech. 2:6 (6–7)","ot/zech/2.6"],"."]]]," winds, from one end of heaven to the other."]],[8,["Send forth the elders of my church unto the ",["nations",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Missionary Work","tg/missionary-work"],"; ",["Nations","tg/nations"],"."]]]," which are afar off; unto the ",["islands",["study-note-ref","b",[["Isa. 11:11",